{"tid":333524,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"將回覆掣放番係下面","createTime":"2017-07-24T01:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T01:23:03.000Z","uid":3290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7074c83efb4a2d7c42d832f52702da00433a5f","tid":333524,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:03:04.000Z","msg":"明明之前個三粒掣（取消、預覽、回覆 / 發表）都係下面，做咩依家放到最上<br />\n好唔方便喎，可唔可以放番係下面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/090149_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F090149_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=6601f246&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f688b441f7d39d98e0ca47cd7817ee71c03a767c","tid":333524,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6137d4ea6d5d376d904bd4691fb3696d9ccc14","tid":333524,"uid":3,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"好多人反映 mobile 版如果放下面會撳錯，所以放左喺上面<br />\ndesktop 版係放下面的，巴打會唔會較到個 screen size 太細？"},{"pid":"ca683cb724a917c30ced67770e8a10abae90ff01","tid":333524,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人反映 mobile 版如果放下面會撳錯，所以放左喺上面<br />\ndesktop 版係放下面的，巴打會唔會較到個 screen size 太細？</blockquote><br />\n我係公司用，所以較細左<br />\n<br />\n有無得mobile同desktop版唔同呀<br />\nDesktop放係上面好唔方便<br />\n<br />\n又或者有無得自己揀放上定放下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20982b732194c53a2876145b9de790f7f1fd6bc","tid":333524,"uid":3,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人反映 mobile 版如果放下面會撳錯，所以放左喺上面<br />\ndesktop 版係放下面的，巴打會唔會較到個 screen size 太細？</blockquote><br />\n我係公司用，所以較細左<br />\n<br />\n有無得mobile同desktop版唔同呀<br />\nDesktop放係上面好唔方便<br />\n<br />\n又或者有無得自己揀放上定放下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你較返大少少應該會見到去返下面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再諗下點解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c783a2d24939278da6e486a8d3678af9bac5e8","tid":333524,"uid":410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"BAN人未呀ADMIN<br />\n網賺撚你又唔撚BAN"},{"pid":"b878fcf8b632cc5d85b38d8cf22153c3afd44bc6","tid":333524,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人反映 mobile 版如果放下面會撳錯，所以放左喺上面<br />\ndesktop 版係放下面的，巴打會唔會較到個 screen size 太細？</blockquote><br />\n回覆人地既 icon 都放下邊啦,<br />\n<br />\n有時睇完D reply 想回覆又要掃翻上上邊個回覆頂先搵到個回覆 icon, 唔方便."},{"pid":"5d0c83dbd7f087bc29ccc0c3f3d88838e791d9cd","tid":333524,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人反映 mobile 版如果放下面會撳錯，所以放左喺上面<br />\ndesktop 版係放下面的，巴打會唔會較到個 screen size 太細？</blockquote><br />\n回覆人地既 icon 都放下邊啦,<br />\n<br />\n有時睇完D reply 想回覆又要掃翻上上邊個回覆頂先搵到個回覆 icon, 唔方便.</blockquote><br />\n諗諗佢啦,  thank you."},{"pid":"5fe0077d55fd161db7fed56848f8bdc3859c4c4f","tid":333524,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好多人反映 mobile 版如果放下面會撳錯，所以放左喺上面<br />\ndesktop 版係放下面的，巴打會唔會較到個 screen size 太細？</blockquote><br />\n我係公司用，所以較細左<br />\n<br />\n有無得mobile同desktop版唔同呀<br />\nDesktop放係上面好唔方便<br />\n<br />\n又或者有無得自己揀放上定放下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你較返大少少應該會見到去返下面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再諗下點解決 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然話就話有扮工模式，不過始終都係返工上網，唔想咁張揚<br />\n果個size我覺得太大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時用住頭殼頂呢個先啦，希望會改改佢，唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}